{# description: Generates a CRM note from email thread context for contact enrichment #}

Generate a CRM activity note from the following email interaction. This note will be written to the Zoho CRM contact record.

RULES:
- note_text must not contain email addresses, phone numbers, or names (use "the customer" / "the contact")
- note_text must be under 150 words
- note_type: one of: INBOUND_INQUIRY | QUOTE_DISCUSSION | SUPPORT_INTERACTION | GENERAL_CONTACT | ORDER_UPDATE
- requires_follow_up: true if the interaction suggests Brad should take a further action
- follow_up_hint: brief action description if requires_follow_up is true, otherwise null
- Do not infer information not present in the source; log only what explicitly occurred

THREAD ID: {{ thread_id }}
CATEGORY: {{ category }}
INTERACTION DATE: {{ interaction_date_utc }}
CONTACT ID: {{ contact_id }}

